Usage: convertFenceToLef [-help] <hinst> [<ptnName>]

-help                # Prints out the command usage
<hinst>              # Specifies the hierarchical instance cell name.
                     # (string, required)
<ptnName>            # Specifies the partition name. If this is not specified,
                     # the command uses the hierarchical instance cell name as
                     # the partition name. (string, optional)